<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-of-justice-northern-ireland> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Department of Justice (Northern Ireland) has a range of powers relating to devolved policing, and is responsible for the resourcing, legislative and policy framework of the justice system in Northern Ireland. DoJ (NI) works with the Northern Ireland Executive and is supported by 8 agencies and public bodies ."@en .
